      Phase 5R revised scope (spec.md Â§"Phase 5+7 Revised Scope" FR-58). FR-52 introduces `NodeType.DeliverComposite` in `PlaybookExecutionEngine` (built in tasks 114b/114c). This task is the proof-point migration: rewrite the production-bound `summarize-document-for-workspace@v1` to use composition. The chat sibling stays single-action because per-section streaming offers no benefit for the chat surface â€” chat continues to emit `FieldDelta` events (FR-53 backward-compat invariant). Migration is Dataverse-data only (no `.cs` changes); the engine support landed in 114b/114c.
    </background>
